# Canonical Map

## Purpose

This document identifies the canonical location of every major concept within Project FAR.

Each concept should have exactly one authoritative definition.

All other documents should reference the canonical source rather than redefining the concept.

This policy minimizes redundancy and prevents inconsistent definitions from developing over time.

